OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fcloudy for Northern Ireland and
OL,7,Fnorthern Scotland with light and
OL,8,Fpatchy drizzle, mostly around coasts
OL,9,Fand hills. Dry and clear elsewhere and
OL,10,Fmuch cooler than recently in the south.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FCloudier than recent days,
OL,13,Fthough sunny spells will develop
OL,14,Fthrough the afternoon. Cloudiest in
OL,15,Fthe north and northwest, with some
OL,16,Flight rain or showers. Warm in central
OL,17,Fand southern Britain.
